                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for preparing carbon black and hydrogen through thermal cracking of hydrocarbon",
                    "一种热裂解烃制备碳黑与氢气的装置及其方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The device comprises a main body, the main body is sequentially provided with a reaction cavity and a carbon black bed from top to bottom, a gas outlet is formed in the upper end of the reaction cavity, a microwave generator is arranged on the side wall of the reaction cavity, an electric heater is arranged on the upper side of the carbon black bed, and a gas outlet is formed in the upper end of the electric heater. An air inlet is formed in the lower end of the carbon black bed. The carbon black bed is preheated by microwaves, then the carbon black bed is jointly heated by microwave heating and electric heating to become a heat source for cracking raw material gas, impurities are not introduced into a reaction system, and the grown new carbon black can be ensured to be high-purity and low-ash carbon black."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种热裂解烃制备碳黑与氢气的装置及其方法，包括主体，所述主体从上到下依次设置有反应腔和碳黑床，所述反应腔上端设置有出气口，所述反应腔侧壁设置有微波发生器，所述碳黑床上侧设置有电加热器，所述碳黑床下端设置有进气口。以微波预加热碳黑床，随后微波加热和电加热共同加热碳黑床使之成为裂解原料气体的热源，也不会向反应体系中引入杂质，可以保证生长出的新碳黑为高纯度、低灰分碳黑。"
                }
            ]
        }
